# MyHeadlines — Environment Variables (all optional)
# All settings are configured through the Setup page in the web UI.
# These environment variables serve as optional overrides.

# ── Server ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PORT=3456

# ── Data Directory ────────────────────────────────────────
# Default: %LOCALAPPDATA%\MyHeadlines (Windows), ~/MyHeadlines (Mac/Linux)
# MYHEADLINES_DATA_DIR=
